# Canonical per-section CI reports (written by run_tests.sh / Dockerfile.*) are
# committed. Ad-hoc / host-run reports auto-named by tests/conftest.py are
# ignored so they never clutter commits.
*
!.gitignore
!offline.xml
!sensors.xml
!mlops.xml
!analytics.xml
!governance.xml
!services.xml
!pipeline.xml
!detchamber.xml
!siem.xml
